########## genatr ##########

Add To Every thing
  Is
    int_attr  42.
End Add To.


The l Isa location
  
  Description
    "Here we have int_attr ="
    Say int_attr Of Current Location.
    "$$."
  
End The l.

The o Isa object
  At l 
End The o.

The hero Isa actor
  
  Has 
    int_attr  96.
End The hero.

Verb v
  Does
    "Location ="
    Say int_attr Of Current Location.
    "$nObject ="
    Say int_attr Of o.
    Increase int_attr Of o.
    "$nHero ="
    Say int_attr Of hero.
End Verb.


Start At l.
  "Try the v verb on the o. LOCATION should have 42, Hero 96 and Object
   from 42 and counting."
  
